/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds. On either side of the road, lush green trees and bushes add a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many urban areas. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene and highlighting the vibrant colors of the cityscape.
